public class Solution {
  public ListNode insert(ListNode head, int target) {
    ListNode newTarget = new ListNode(target);
    if (head == null) {
      return newTarget;
    }else if (head.value > target) {
      newTarget.next = head;
      return newTarget;
    }
    ListNode left = head;
    while (left.value < target && left.next != null && left.next.value < target) {
      left = left.next;
    }
    ListNode temp = left.next;
    left.next = newTarget;
    newTarget.next = temp;
    return head;
  }
}



注意的点：
1. 新建ListNode格式不能忘 ListNode xxx = new ListNode();
2. ListNode and int share the name pool in one method, so never duplicate the variable name
3. always remember dereference can not be null, so 'left.next != null' then check value is very important.
